message: "If you use AURA, please cite the associated paper and this software artifact."
title: "AURA: Auditable UI-Mediated Android Evidence Acquisition"
type: software
authors:
  - name: "AURA contributors"
date-released: 2026-06-05
abstract: "AURA is a UI-mediated Android evidence acquisition research prototype that records reviewable audit trails, normalized evidence records, and acquisition-context linkage for app-visible mobile messenger data collection."
